author: eTN Global Editor
title: Southwest Airlines declares 156th consecutive quarterly dividend
text:
Southwest Airlines declares 156th consecutive quarterly dividend Adv: 
Jul 30, 2015 Adv: 
DALLAS, TX - Southwest Airlines' Board of Directors declared a quarterly dividend of $.075 per share to Shareholders of record at the close of business on August 20, 2015 on all shares then issued and outstanding. The 156th consecutive dividend will be paid on September 10, 2015.
